WEBVTT

00:00.868 --> 00:03.637
[ DRAMATIC MUSIC PLAYS ]

00:31.165 --> 00:33.234
[ WIND HOWLING ]

00:33.234 --> 00:35.369
[ ENGINE REVVING ]

00:53.587 --> 00:55.289
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

00:57.158 --> 01:00.394
[ AIR HISSING ]

01:11.939 --> 01:14.074
[ SOBS ]
AAH!

01:14.074 --> 01:18.612
SOUTHLAND COPS KNOW
WHEN THE SANTA ANA WINDS BLOW,

01:18.612 --> 01:21.349
YOU LEARN JUST HOW CLOSE
YOU ARE TO THE EDGE.

01:22.183 --> 01:23.717
[ LAUGHS ]

01:25.219 --> 01:26.587
AW.
OHH.

01:26.587 --> 01:27.688
[ WIND HOWLING ]

01:27.688 --> 01:30.023
SANTA ANAS
ARE BLOWING OUT MY 'DO.

01:30.023 --> 01:32.226
I HAD TO RUN
HALFWAY DOWN THE STREET

01:32.226 --> 01:33.961
TO GET
MY RECYCLING BIN.

01:33.961 --> 01:35.696
I DON'T GET IT.

01:35.696 --> 01:37.698
IT USED TO BE JUST THREE MONTHS
OUT OF THE YEAR THE WINDS BLEW.

01:37.698 --> 01:40.000
NOW IT'S LIKE FIRE SEASON
ALL YEAR ROUND.

01:40.000 --> 01:41.869
ADAMS.

01:41.869 --> 01:44.638
