HIT ANOTHER VICTIM.

01:44.638 --> 01:46.006
DAMN.

01:46.006 --> 01:50.744
ARE YOU EXPERIENCING ANY RELIEF
FROM YOUR SYMPTOMS?

01:50.744 --> 01:52.045
NO.

01:52.045 --> 01:55.683
NOT REALLY.

01:55.683 --> 01:56.884
WELL, IF IT'S
NOT HELPING BY NOW,

01:56.884 --> 01:59.553
IT'S PROBABLY NOT MUSCULAR.

01:59.553 --> 02:01.789
YOUR INSURANCE
ONLY COVERS 12 SESSIONS.

02:01.789 --> 02:02.956
