TO LOOK INTO OTHER OPTIONS.

02:13.201 --> 02:16.136
HAVE YOU THOUGHT
ABOUT SURGERY?

02:16.136 --> 02:18.972
LOOK, IT'S YOUR BACK.

02:18.972 --> 02:20.641
IF IT WAS MY BACK,

02:20.641 --> 02:23.677
