02:27.581 --> 02:29.550
HEY.

02:29.550 --> 02:31.919
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS ]
[ SIGHS ]

02:31.919 --> 02:34.087
EVERY WOMAN'S
WORST NIGHTMARE.

02:34.087 --> 02:35.689
