FROM A BUSINESS TRIP...
MM.

02:37.658 --> 02:39.993
...FOUND HIS WIFE ROUGHED UP
AND PRETTY HYSTERICAL.

02:39.993 --> 02:41.662
ANY SIGNS
OF FORCED ENTRY?

02:41.662 --> 02:43.096
