THAT TORN WINDOW SCREEN.

02:43.096 --> 02:44.432
THAT'S ALL WE GOT.

02:44.432 --> 02:46.367
HMM. WITNESSES?

02:46.367 --> 02:48.602
MIDDLE OF THE NIGHT --
MAID WASN'T WORKING.

02:48.602 --> 02:50.438
SO, DID YOU TALK
TO THE VICTIM?

02:50.438 --> 02:52.240
NO. I TRIED,
BUT SHE'S PRETTY TRAUMATIZED.

02:52.240 --> 02:54.141
