CAN TALK TO HER.

02:54.141 --> 02:56.310
YEAH, LET'S GET A CANVASS
GOING IN THE NEIGHBORHOOD,
ALL RIGHT?

02:56.310 --> 02:57.745
OKAY, OKAY.
THANKS.

02:57.745 --> 02:59.280
[ WIND HOWLING ]

03:00.781 --> 03:04.051
I BEGGED HIM
NOT TO CALL THE POLICE.

03:04.051 --> 03:07.187
MRS. WELLINGTON, I KNOW
THIS IS DIFFICULT FOR YOU,

03:07.187 --> 03:09.890
BUT WE NEED TO ASK YOU
A COUPLE OF QUESTIONS.

03:14.127 --> 03:15.629
I'M SURE YOU THINK
YOU DON'T HAVE

03:15.629 --> 03:17.598
THE STRENGTH TO DO THIS,
BUT YOU DO.

03:17.598 --> 03:18.832
I DON'T.

03:18.832 --> 03:20.534
YOU'RE GONNA
GET THROUGH THIS.

03:20.534 --> 03:22.936
I'LL PUT YOU IN TOUCH
WITH SOME PEOPLE THAT I KNOW

03:22.936 --> 03:24.805
AT THE RAPE TREATMENT CENTER
WHO CAN HELP YOU.

03:24.805 --> 03:26.240
YOU KNOW,
THIS NEVER WOULD HAVE HAPPENED

03:26.240 --> 03:27.875
IF I WASN'T TRAVELING
SO MUCH.

03:27.875 --> 03:32.380
OH, THIS ISN'T YOUR FAULT.
IT'S NOBODY'S FAULT.

03:32.380 --> 03:34.982
LOOK, I KNOW YOU DON'T THINK
YOU CAN TALK RIGHT NOW,

03:34.982 --> 03:37.951
BUT WE THINK THAT YOU COULD BE
THIS MAN'S FOURTH VICTIM.

03:37.951 --> 03:40.521
AND THERE ARE A LOT
OF OTHER WOMEN OUT THERE,

03:40.521 --> 03:43.724
AND I DON'T WANT TO SEE THE SAME
THING TO HAPPEN TO THEM.

03:43.724 --> 03:45.125
DO YOU?

03:45.125 --> 03:47.361
NO.

03:47.361 --> 03:49.229
THEN HELP US STOP HIM.

03:49.229 --> 03:52.165
[ SIGHS ]

03:52.165 --> 03:54.535
IT WAS DARK.

03:54.535 --> 03:56.737
I WOKE UP,
AND HE WAS ON TOP OF ME.

03:56.737 --> 03:59.139
Lydia:
DID YOU SEE HIS FACE?

03:59.139 --> 04:01.141
NOT VERY WELL.

04:01.141 --> 04:03.344
IT WAS DARK.

04:03.344 --> 04:05.879
WHAT WAS HE WEARING?

04:05.879 --> 04:08.849
SOME KIND OF UNIFORM.

04:08.849 --> 04:12.119
DID IT SAY ANYTHING,
HAVE A COMPANY NAME?

04:12.119 --> 04:18.091
NO, JUST T-THE TYPE JANITORS
WEAR, PEOPLE LIKE THAT.

04:18.091 --> 04:20.428
WHAT COLOR?

04:20.428 --> 04:23.864
IT WAS DARK.

04:23.864 --> 04:26.900
GREEN.

04:26.900 --> 04:31.271
BLUE. I...

04:31.271 --> 04:34.775
DID -- DID HE SAY
ANYTHING TO YOU?

04:38.379 --> 04:41.715
